  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div><include href=\"../Passage/VR856258.qti.xml\" xmlns:xi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude\"></include></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">The image formed by the mirror has a height of magnitude <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"h sub P\"><math alttext=\"h sub P\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><msub><mi>h</mi><mtext>P</mtext></msub></mstyle></math></span></span> when the object is at Point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"P\"><math alttext=\"P\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>P</mtext></math></span></span>. If the object is moved to Point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Q\"><math alttext=\"Q\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>Q</mtext></math></span></span>, twice as far from the mirror as Point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"P\"><math alttext=\"P\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>P</mtext></math></span></span>, how does the new image height magnitude <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"h sub Q\"><math alttext=\"h sub Q\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><msub><mi>h</mi><mtext>Q</mtext></msub></mstyle></math></span></span> compare to <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"h sub P\"><math alttext=\"h sub P\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><msub><mi>h</mi><mtext>P</mtext></msub></mstyle></math></span></span>?</p>\n",
    "answer": "i2",
    "choices": [
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"h sub Q, is less than one half h sub P\"><math alttext=\"h sub Q, is less than one half h sub P\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><msub><mi>h</mi><mtext>Q</mtext></msub><mo>&lt;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msub><mi>h</mi><mtext>P</mtext></msub></mstyle></math></span></span></p>",
        "value": "i1"
      },
